name: 达希尔·墨西特
name_full: 达希尔·墨西特 Dashiell Messitt

last_movies.title: 危险特工队 第一季
欢乐再满屋 第一季

introduction: Dashiell is an identical twin to Fox Messitt. They were born in December 2014 in Burbank, CA. They have been appearing on screen since 2 months of age in National TV commercials and hit TV shows such as Fuller House, Grey's Anatomy and Danger Force. They enjoy acting and modeling as well as karate, gymnastics, snow skiing, ice skating and horseback riding. They are involved in Cub Scouts and love to make art. They are learning Spanish in an immersion program at school.When he and Fox started at 7 months old, they didn't even know how to crawl. And in the process of doing the show they started crawling and started walking.
